# Building Supply Store API

## Brick Type [/bricks/{id}]

+ Parameters
  + id: XYZ42 - ID of a brick type.
+ Attributes
  + id
  + name (string)
  + colors: red, brown (array)
  + dimensions (array)
    + *20, 30, 40* (array[number], fixed)

### Get Particular Brick Type [GET]

+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
  + Attributes (Brick Type)

## Available Brick Types [/bricks]

### List Available Brick Types [GET]

+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
  + Attributes (array[Brick Type])
